{"word":"Self-Delusion","slug":"self-delusion","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Self-Delusion</b> A characteristic of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=49&verse=18'>Psa 49:18</a><br/> Prosperity frequently leads to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=30&verse=6'>Psa 30:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=12&verse=8'>Hos 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=19'>Luk 12:19</a><br/> Obstinate sinners often given up to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=12'>Psa 81:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=17'>Hos 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=53&chapter=2&verse=11'>2Th 2:11</a><br/> Exhibited in thinking that:<br/> - Our own ways are right<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=14&verse=12'>Pro 14:12</a> <br/> - We should adhere to established wicked practices<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=44&verse=17'>Jer 44:17</a> <br/> - We are pure<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=12'>Pro 30:12</a> <br/> - We are better than others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=11'>Luk 18:11</a> <br/> - We are rich in spiritual things<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=3&verse=17'>Rev 3:17</a> <br/> - We may have peace while in sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=19'>Deu 29:19</a> <br/> - We are above adversity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=10&verse=6'>Psa 10:6</a> <br/> - Gifts entitle us to heaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=7&verse=22'>Mat 7:22</a> <br/> - Privileges entitle us to heaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=9'>Mat 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=26'>Luk 13:26</a> <br/> - God will not punish our sins<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=5&verse=12'>Jer 5:12</a> <br/> - Christ will not come to judge<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=3&verse=4'>2Pe 3:4</a> <br/> - Our lives will be prolonged<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=56&verse=12'>Isa 56:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=19'>Luk 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=4&verse=13'>Jas 4:13</a> <br/> Frequently persevered in self-delusion to the last<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=7&verse=22'>Mat 7:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=12'>Mat 25:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=25'>Luk 13:25</a><br/> Fatal consequences of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=7&verse=23'>Mat 7:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=51'>Mat 24:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=20'>Luk 12:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=3'>1Th 5:3</a><br/> Exemplified:<br/> - Ahab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=27'>1Ki 20:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=34'>1Ki 20:34</a> <br/> - Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=12&verse=8'>Hos 12:8</a> <br/> - Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=8&verse=33'>Joh 8:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=8&verse=41'>Joh 8:41</a> <br/> - Church of Laodicea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=3&verse=17'>Rev 3:17</a><br/><a href='S:Confidence, False'>Confidence, False</a>; <a href='S:Security, False'>Security, False</a> "}]}